## Job Status Lifecycle

```
UNDER_CONSTRUCTION → INFO_GATHERING → UNCLAIMED → CLAIMED → [ON_HOLD/IDLE] → CLOSED
```

| Status | Description | Payment State |
|--------|-------------|---------------|
| `UNDER_CONSTRUCTION` | Customer answering intake questions | **Not paid** |
| `INFO_GATHERING` | Customer uploading documents for Tax Pro | Paid |
| `UNCLAIMED` | Job in queue, waiting for Tax Pro to claim | Paid |
| `CLAIMED` | Tax Pro has picked up the job | Paid |
| `ON_HOLD` | Job paused (various reasons) | Paid |
| `IDLE` | Job inactive | Paid |
| `CLOSED` | Job completed | Paid (full amount) |

### Key Insight: Payment Indicator

**Any status other than `UNDER_CONSTRUCTION` means the customer has paid.**

