## Payment Structure

| Field | Description |
|-------|-------------|
| `total` | Full job price (what the customer will pay in total) |
| `paid_amount` | Amount collected so far (typically 50% at submission) |
| `coupon_amount` | Discount applied |
| `provider_cut_amount` | Amount allocated to the Tax Pro |

### Payment Timeline

1. **At submission**: 50% of `total` is charged → populates `paid_amount`
2. **At close**: Remaining 50% is charged → `paid_amount` equals `total`

