## Sample Queries (BigQuery / Metabase)

### Sales Today (TAX Jobs)

```sql
SELECT COUNT(*) as sales_today
FROM dbt_models.fct_jobs
WHERE type = 'TAX'
    AND workspace_class IN ('B2C', 'B2B2C')
    AND DATE(DATETIME(date_first_submitted, 'America/New_York')) = DATE(DATETIME(CURRENT_TIMESTAMP(), 'America/New_York'))
```

### Sales Yesterday

```sql
SELECT COUNT(*) as sales_yesterday
FROM dbt_models.fct_jobs
WHERE type = 'TAX'
    AND workspace_class IN ('B2C', 'B2B2C')
    AND DATE(DATETIME(date_first_submitted, 'America/New_York')) = DATE_SUB(DATE(DATETIME(CURRENT_TIMESTAMP(), 'America/New_York')), INTERVAL 1 DAY)
```

### Season to Date (STD) Sales & Revenue

```sql
SELECT
    COUNT(*) as sales_std,
    SUM(total) as revenue_std
FROM dbt_models.fct_jobs
WHERE type = 'TAX'
    AND workspace_class IN ('B2C', 'B2B2C')
    AND DATE(DATETIME(date_first_submitted, 'America/New_York')) >= '2026-01-19'
```

### Sales by Partner (Today vs Yesterday)

```sql
SELECT
    workspace_name as partner_name,
    SUM(CASE WHEN DATE(DATETIME(date_first_submitted, 'America/New_York')) = DATE_SUB(DATE(DATETIME(CURRENT_TIMESTAMP(), 'America/New_York')), INTERVAL 1 DAY) THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) as sales_yesterday,
    SUM(CASE WHEN DATE(DATETIME(date_first_submitted, 'America/New_York')) = DATE(DATETIME(CURRENT_TIMESTAMP(), 'America/New_York')) THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) as sales_today
FROM dbt_models.fct_jobs
WHERE type = 'TAX'
    AND workspace_class IN ('B2C', 'B2B2C')
    AND DATE(DATETIME(date_first_submitted, 'America/New_York')) >= DATE_SUB(DATE(DATETIME(CURRENT_TIMESTAMP(), 'America/New_York')), INTERVAL 1 DAY)
GROUP BY workspace_name
ORDER BY sales_yesterday DESC
```

### Hourly Cumulative (Today vs Yesterday) - Ritmo por Hora

```sql
SELECT
    hour_miami,
    SUM(SUM(CASE WHEN day_flag = 'today' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END)) OVER (ORDER BY hour_miami) as cumulative_today,
    SUM(SUM(CASE WHEN day_flag = 'yesterday' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END)) OVER (ORDER BY hour_miami) as cumulative_yesterday
FROM (
    SELECT
        EXTRACT(HOUR FROM DATETIME(date_first_submitted, 'America/New_York')) as hour_miami,
        CASE
            WHEN DATE(DATETIME(date_first_submitted, 'America/New_York')) = DATE(DATETIME(CURRENT_TIMESTAMP(), 'America/New_York')) THEN 'today'
            WHEN DATE(DATETIME(date_first_submitted, 'America/New_York')) = DATE_SUB(DATE(DATETIME(CURRENT_TIMESTAMP(), 'America/New_York')), INTERVAL 1 DAY) THEN 'yesterday'
        END as day_flag
    FROM dbt_models.fct_jobs
    WHERE type = 'TAX'
        AND workspace_class IN ('B2C', 'B2B2C')
        AND DATE(DATETIME(date_first_submitted, 'America/New_York')) >= DATE_SUB(DATE(DATETIME(CURRENT_TIMESTAMP(), 'America/New_York')), INTERVAL 1 DAY)
) sub
GROUP BY hour_miami
ORDER BY hour_miami
```

### Year-over-Year Cumulative (2026 vs 2025)

```sql
WITH daily_sales AS (
    SELECT
        EXTRACT(YEAR FROM DATETIME(date_first_submitted, 'America/New_York')) as year,
        EXTRACT(DAYOFYEAR FROM DATETIME(date_first_submitted, 'America/New_York')) as day_of_year,
        COUNT(*) as daily_jobs
    FROM dbt_models.fct_jobs
    WHERE type = 'TAX'
        AND workspace_class IN ('B2C', 'B2B2C')
        AND (
            (EXTRACT(YEAR FROM DATETIME(date_first_submitted, 'America/New_York')) = 2025
             AND EXTRACT(DAYOFYEAR FROM DATETIME(date_first_submitted, 'America/New_York')) <= EXTRACT(DAYOFYEAR FROM DATETIME(CURRENT_TIMESTAMP(), 'America/New_York')))
            OR
            (EXTRACT(YEAR FROM DATETIME(date_first_submitted, 'America/New_York')) = 2026
             AND EXTRACT(DAYOFYEAR FROM DATETIME(date_first_submitted, 'America/New_York')) <= EXTRACT(DAYOFYEAR FROM DATETIME(CURRENT_TIMESTAMP(), 'America/New_York')))
        )
    GROUP BY year, day_of_year
)
SELECT
    day_of_year,
    SUM(CASE WHEN year = 2026 THEN daily_jobs ELSE 0 END) as jobs_2026,
    SUM(CASE WHEN year = 2025 THEN daily_jobs ELSE 0 END) as jobs_2025,
    SUM(SUM(CASE WHEN year = 2026 THEN daily_jobs ELSE 0 END)) OVER (ORDER BY day_of_year) as cumulative_2026,
    SUM(SUM(CASE WHEN year = 2025 THEN daily_jobs ELSE 0 END)) OVER (ORDER BY day_of_year) as cumulative_2025
FROM daily_sales
GROUP BY day_of_year
ORDER BY day_of_year
```

### YoY Partner Performance - All B2C/B2B2C

Chart name: `YoY Partner Performance - Season to Date`
Description: `Compara jobs por partner: 2026 vs mismo período 2025. Diff negativo = behind last year.`

```sql
SELECT
    CASE
        WHEN workspace_id = 323 THEN 'Rocket Lawyer'
        ELSE workspace_name
    END as partner_name,
    workspace_id,
    SUM(CASE WHEN EXTRACT(YEAR FROM DATETIME(date_first_submitted, 'America/New_York')) = 2026 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) as jobs_2026,
    SUM(CASE WHEN EXTRACT(YEAR FROM DATETIME(date_first_submitted, 'America/New_York')) = 2025 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) as jobs_2025,
    SUM(CASE WHEN EXTRACT(YEAR FROM DATETIME(date_first_submitted, 'America/New_York')) = 2026 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END)
    - SUM(CASE WHEN EXTRACT(YEAR FROM DATETIME(date_first_submitted, 'America/New_York')) = 2025 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) as diff,
    ROUND(
        SAFE_DIVIDE(
            SUM(CASE WHEN EXTRACT(YEAR FROM DATETIME(date_first_submitted, 'America/New_York')) = 2026 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END),
            SUM(CASE WHEN EXTRACT(YEAR FROM DATETIME(date_first_submitted, 'America/New_York')) = 2025 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END)
        ) * 100, 1
    ) as pct_of_last_year
FROM dbt_models.fct_jobs
WHERE type = 'TAX'
    AND workspace_class IN ('B2C', 'B2B2C')
    AND (
        (EXTRACT(YEAR FROM DATETIME(date_first_submitted, 'America/New_York')) = 2025
         AND EXTRACT(DAYOFYEAR FROM DATETIME(date_first_submitted, 'America/New_York')) <= EXTRACT(DAYOFYEAR FROM DATETIME(CURRENT_TIMESTAMP(), 'America/New_York')))
        OR
        (EXTRACT(YEAR FROM DATETIME(date_first_submitted, 'America/New_York')) = 2026
         AND EXTRACT(DAYOFYEAR FROM DATETIME(date_first_submitted, 'America/New_York')) <= EXTRACT(DAYOFYEAR FROM DATETIME(CURRENT_TIMESTAMP(), 'America/New_York')))
    )
GROUP BY partner_name, workspace_id
ORDER BY diff ASC
```

