### YoY Comparison Notes

When comparing year-over-year:
- Use `EXTRACT(DAYOFYEAR FROM ...)` to align same calendar days
- Filter both years up to the current day of year to ensure fair comparison
- Example: On January 21, 2026, compare days 1-21 of both 2025 and 2026
